data.title: 50 war classics. Disc 5
data.meta_description: Side A. Kansas Pacific: Re-enactment of the problems that occurred during the construction of the Kansas Pacific Railroad -- Three come home: Story of Agnes Newton Keith's imprisonment in Japan prison camps during World War II -- The avenger: Story of Aeneas, hero of the fall of Troy and the birth of Rome -- The torch: A Mexican town is controlled by a revolutionary who is both adored and disliked by the townspeople -- The air war: Portrays the importance of aid from the U.S. Air Force against Nazi air attacks.
